\
\cf10 \cb3 \strokec10       const perDigit = total / 9;\cf4 \cb1 \strokec4 \
\cf10 \cb3 \strokec10       digitIndex = Math.min(8, Math.floor(elapsed / perDigit));\cf4 \cb1 \strokec4 \
